Formresponses1.description: Junkyard 2.0 is a fun event where participants can test their knowledge of electronics. In event consist of 2 rounds. Round 1 is a puzzle round where students have to complete a crossword in 2 min. Round 2 will be Find From the Junk round where students have to search instrument from the junk in 5min.

A part of the free time of the students goes to  these TV series. So this event dealing with them will take their attention away from their routine lives for sometime.

This event is basically a quiz competition based on popular TV Series. The event begins with a screening process and selected teams will go through the quiz. Winners of each round will get prizes whose worth increases with each round.

Level 1 audio-visual round
Level 2 Damsharas
Level 3 Rapidfire

A three round coding contest comsisting of blind coding, rearranging jumbled code and a decoding treasure hunt.
COUNTER STRIKE :The evergreen passion of any gamer. Come and enjoy uninterrupted gaming session and win exciting prizes.

CODE SHOOT
Be part of a shooting game and hone your logic and technical skills all while having fun at the same time, where you target at a prop, that individually represents a question that will be presented on your page, of any of the selected difficulties. Select, shoot, and bag a prize!

The 1st round of an event consist of MCQ type questions focused on the trending and famous technology and invention through out history of science. Winners of 1st round are further go in the next round which consist of interactive type session (Buzzer round, Rapid Fire round, Technological games and many more interesting rounds). The winners of an event are provided with certificate and interesting prizes.
(All branches students are eligible)

Firstly, assemble all the pieces of Jigsaw Puzzle to form a required picture of the circuit to be made. Find out all the components by the given clues hidden in different places inside the campus. Using all the components make a working circuit. The team finishing this 'CIRCUIT HUNT RACE'' will be the winner.
